Steps for running the scripts:
1. clone the source code from github
2. open this as new project by using Intellij
3. once all file has been synced up, go to "View->Tool Windows->Gradle".
4. Go to "Tasks->build", click "clean" first, then click "build". then all test scenarios will be started.
5. after all cases finished, please go to "out" folder to check the test result.